</title>
<subSubSection id="8C5DF73AE10539780EE55C4BAE8353FC" pageId="null" pageNumber="596" type="description">
<paragraph id="66716BF27F52AAACE30373D3B1E5AACE" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="3641DF74EC7B13BADBB2E9D32121EA02" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Vicia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="596" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="DE931D6E7FC77AE97109D1A23BEFAA66" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">Vicia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(S. 576) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="2F66CD607EEE455539426204328ABAFD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">
<normalizedToken id="151EDF2B67759099211848B2F0EEB7DD" originalValue="Kelchzähne" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">Kelchzaehne</normalizedToken>
mehr als doppelt so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="DF3CF43CAFF81251E593C25BD6353F70" originalValue="Kelchröhre" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">Kelchroehre</normalizedToken>
. Schiffchen gerade, spitz, oft etwas 
<normalizedToken id="84294AADD8100689257EB0ADA069705B" originalValue="geschnäbelt" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">geschnaebelt</normalizedToken>
;
</emphasis>
Frucht 2-, seltener 1 
<normalizedToken id="13233A00FADDEAA42024D61FC66C92AB" originalValue="sämig" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">saemig</normalizedToken>
; Samen flach (
<normalizedToken id="F854E357DD5B3E5D9E0BD58552C9CF0D" originalValue="linsenförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">linsenfoermig</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="529951579F1448E18FC691A813859F2A" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">
Die Gattung 
<taxonomicName id="5D90E5FAC8D4EC22A6200F6E9C5C3280" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Lens" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="596" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="DDE09F147262E4F186270B4829E75B33" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">Lens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="90E16C549D7D726A42EF08F6EDA5B6C8" originalValue="umfaßt" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">umfasst</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="DC128BF4B18943D17609C2D6ABE6AEBC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">6 Arten und hat vor allem ostmediterrane Verbreitung.</emphasis>
Die Abtrennung von 
<taxonomicName id="5C06A56D38B6B7E7A6F78449DE049D63" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Lens" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="596" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="7DAE23D99C8EED4EB13828E8BC79DB92" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">Lens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
als eigene Gattung 
<normalizedToken id="002A23DEA52ADF907FA63095ADB3BBE7" originalValue="gegenüber" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">gegenueber</normalizedToken>
<taxonomicName id="18982356EB8ED0CCC32E96A097BA80C8" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Vicia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="596" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="F47482F444D18C41423FE08D7C0E2A6B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">Vicia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, die fast 
<normalizedToken id="828BD4AF692CA20BFD65272D96419267" originalValue="überall" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">ueberall</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="BD98E3BABF0698ECACE7B31DEF3FAAC0" originalValue="durchgeführt" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">durchgefuehrt</normalizedToken>
wird, ist kaum 
<normalizedToken id="2F015D333F9236F20A6C23E5F84FDE60" originalValue="begründet" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">begruendet</normalizedToken>
, sind doch auch Bastarde mit 
<taxonomicName id="035902EFDFAE6E40F0F1FF344A2C8165" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Vicia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="596" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="D58E5BFEC4FF2F629CA0F40815D0F7C8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">Vicia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
bekannt: 
<taxonomicName id="48FBE8D1D47D5EE03B4F13B82DC9B93E" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Lens" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="596" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="culinaris">
<emphasis id="A5B0FB1CD4F770068DA6C128D033A152" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">
<authorityName id="EDB273DA753FB311904C1CA482B20B19" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">L.</authorityName>
culinaris
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="4D10D41502F8392D038F4130630B1010" originalValue="×" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">x</normalizedToken>
<taxonomicName id="59F93F5684444CFE2F64BE3E4822E1EC" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Vicia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="596" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sativa">
<emphasis id="553E48D733CCE2A470B65716F0949F7B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="596">V. sativa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Bleier aus Tischler und Wulff 1953-1963).
</paragraph>
